        "name": "Web Credential Creation",
        "url": "/datasources/DS0006/#Web%20Credential%20Creation"
      },
      "description": "Monitor for creation of access tokens using SAML tokens which do not have corresponding 4769 and 1200 events in the domain. Additionally, detect on unusual API calls to generate access tokens, such as sts:GetFederationToken in AWS."
    },
